		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I polished the connectors, I melted the cartridge open (which is pretty painstaking for someone who collects vintage videogames), I even tried quickly holding an open flame under the connectors &amp; polishing them again!  Still the same crap:  Non-blinking blueish-green screen of death.
<br />
<br />This is a TROM cart, w/ 2 caps &amp; 2 resistors.  Would you guys think it could be one of them?  (I don't have the equipment to test them at the moment...)

		

